name: Christa Renz / Historia Reiss Shingeki No Kyojin
description:
A LoRA of Christa Renz / Historia Reiss from AOT. Trained on NAI with 93 images.

See samples for good prompts.

I recommend a weight of 1 for SFW.

Good with anime based models like NAI, AOM3 or Anything v4.5.

A LoRA for the best waifu of AOT.

All of my LoRAs will always be free. If you paid for this or an image using this LoRA, you got scamed! If you wants to supports me, feel free to buy me a Ko-Fi.
